# Teammates: add Supabase keys (Dashboard → Settings → API).
# Easiest: put both in repo ROOT .env.local only (loaded automatically from webapp/).
# If you use this file, fill BOTH lines — empty values here override root and break /room.
# SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=sb_publishable_...

# Optional: legacy JWT anon key works too
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
